---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About | Sambit Maps" 
  description="About Sambit - Complexity researcher, epistemologist, and systems thinker"
  mode="academic"
>
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-header">
      <h1>About Me</h1>
      <p class="about-subtitle">
        Cognitive Science Research Intern and Interpretive social science student
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <section class="bio-section">
        <h2>What I'm Doing</h2>
        <p>
          I'm currently a research intern studying how trilingual people manage three languages 
          in their heads. Most of the research on multilingualism focuses on people who speak two 
          languages, but here in Nepal, lots of people grow up with three (Nepali, English, and Newari), 
          which seems to work differently.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          I'm also teaching myself computational modeling because I keep running into questions 
          that seem like they need computational approaches to understand properly. It's a steep 
          learning curve, but fascinating to see how modeling changes the way you think about problems.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="academic-philosophy">
        <h2>How I Currently Think About Research</h2>
        
        <div class="philosophy-points">
          <div class="philosophy-point">
            <p>
              I started out thinking there should be one 'right' way to do research, but working 
              across different domains taught me that different types of questions genuinely need 
              different approaches. I've learned to hold multiple methodological frameworks 
              simultaneously without falling into relativism - <a href="/notes/critical-realism">critical realist synthesis</a> gives 
              me the ontological foundation to do this coherently.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="current-work">
        <h2>Current Work</h2>
        
        <div class="work-items">
          <div class="work-item">
            <h4>Research Internship</h4>
            <p>
              Studying trilingual cognitive control - how people manage three languages (Nepali, 
              English, Newari) in their heads. Most research focuses on bilingualism, but trilingual 
              processing seems to work differently.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="work-item">
            <h4>Diploma Project</h4>
            <p>
              Writing about what it's like doing cognitive science research in Nepal. How do cultural 
              contexts and institutional differences affect how research actually gets done?
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="work-item">
            <h4>Self-Teaching</h4>
            <p>
              Learning computational modeling and complex systems approaches because I keep hitting 
              questions that seem to need these tools to understand properly.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-section">
      <h2>Connect</h2>
      
      <div class="contact-methods">
        <div class="contact-item">
          <strong>Email:</strong>
          <span>sambit.rimal@theopen.institute</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
  }

  .about-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--secondary);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  section {
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--secondary);
  }

  section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  section p {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .focus-areas {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .focus-area {
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--secondary);
  }

  .focus-area h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .focus-area p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .philosophy-points {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .philosophy-point {
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
  }

  .philosophy-point h4 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .philosophy-point p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .work-items, .community-info {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .work-item, .community-item {
    background: var(--bg);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--secondary);
  }

  .work-item h4, .community-item h4 {
    color: var(--accent);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .work-item p, .community-item p {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .work-item p:last-child, .community-item p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .work-item em {
    color: var(--secondary);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .contact-section {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contact-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    color: white;
  }

  .contact-section p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .contact-methods {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .contact-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-item strong {
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .contact-item span {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    
    .focus-areas {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    section {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .contact-methods {
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .contact-item {
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>